text: I got the wrong turbo I couldn't tell in the picture but this one is for a later 2004 f350 which has the different pedastool so now I have to get that other one. It's not that I want or need a sinister sticker or diesel ops sticker or shirt or receipt or anything but you figure when you spend 1600$ on a turbo you'd at least get a sticker and a receipt
